{"tid":1124592,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"煮撈麵要考牌","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T04:10:40.000Z","uid":161224,"like":111,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d39e99cf3b253b83080430000e8013b927543af6","tid":1124592,"uid":161224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"先唔講 以前7仔五蚊 賣到而家成十蚊個營多撈麵<br />\n講真食得撈麵都係想食啲味精 你老味 成日啲味精同埋醬 未落曬 就抌咗包嘢 一係就剪包味精嘅時候 已經剪咗三分一落垃圾桶 成個撈麵都唔撚夠味精 點過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到麵質 一係就掛住同啲同事傾計 煮到個面淋撚曬 一係就咁麵都未撚熟 就撈起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好我當 麵質個個都唔同要求 大佬講到明營多撈麵 係<strong>撈麵</strong> 你啲水未fing乾就dum落去啲水度 整到淡曬 水汪汪... 都唔知自己係咪食緊湯麵&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話幾蚊個 就唔要求咁多<br />\n而家成十蚊個 畀番少少質素我得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea87ad38a1c3b12c31f0f3c76b867c0b01dc1bd8","tid":1124592,"uid":10397,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"OK果啲反而整得幾好<br />\n加埋個咖哩魚蛋多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cd7f8ff89c870fd01b2065037726b15344c192","tid":1124592,"uid":90820,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"有啲7仔阿姐好鍾意放定晒啲調味料落兜<br />\n啲醬痴晒喺個盒底<br />\n都唔知撈乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06c2a0a90281786ee73cdcd0f1b55773a488e3e","tid":1124592,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"戒左佢啦 無益"},{"pid":"6c4ecc3f16954b37ccf6afb67a9e2a4658a00ec1","tid":1124592,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b273be3578e779157e9b39751928303cebeef049","tid":1124592,"uid":241412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b0122a23a4c1c63e074bbca9a35999585d83a18","tid":1124592,"uid":60092,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"七仔嗰啲算鳩數啦，個個麵都一早淥好哂先。<br />\n到賣俾你嗰陣已經脹到仆街，根本撈乜落去都係食屎咁。<br />\n非連鎖小食店阿姐即煮嗰啲撈麵真係鳩煮都贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b036c62d0cfe472c1dcfe28a58fc6e0fc8a6d04","tid":1124592,"uid":29120,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06fde0df9a16c97489ac3f8be6b8c017223dd5c4","tid":1124592,"uid":80814,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"阿波羅撈得好食啲"},{"pid":"08f0432c3d90a983d410e3861d5db8d411002494","tid":1124592,"uid":43780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"自己整最好食，用微波爐整好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd31034e1d39fbfa1367c6d0af2e3e2b3477127","tid":1124592,"uid":226489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"基本上七仔小食部啲嘢全部都係垃圾級別，寧願叮嘢食好過"},{"pid":"2e609e59212640ff79c9214d76f3dce1e6d15192","tid":1124592,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"淋撚到糊仔咁真係你食埋我嗰份"},{"pid":"4b9e59999908bef1cbce19dfca5bddfb490b9da5","tid":1124592,"uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"好睇人，條友鳩整都無辦法，你咪試下同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8c2b862859c179d754c395e3f772ae38900191","tid":1124592,"uid":250444,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"以前食過OK xo醬撈烏冬(唔知宜家重有冇) 屌打7仔撈面"},{"pid":"d74735a617312870dfcae243e46c9bd47106b666","tid":1124592,"uid":119008,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"做過7仔既同你講<br />\n基本上全部都煮定先 仲要係朝早返工set野果陣就會煮定<br />\n跟住有人黎再放返落去煮熱返<br />\n一定會overcook 淋過毛巾<br />\n如果你一次買幾樣野食 或者有幾條友買野食<br />\n你千奇咪比佢聽到你叫撈麵 聽唔到 就唔好比飛佢住<br />\n等佢搞好其他野先<br />\n如果唔係收到飛 佢第一時間就放左你果個煮過既麵落去煮熱返先<br />\n隔左幾分鐘搞掂其他魚蛋燒賣腸粉碗仔翅 佢先會再搞你個麵<br />\n到時真係入口即融呀屌你個老母<br />\n叫烏冬就一定無撈麵咁伏<br />\n但係營多就係營多 無野取代到<br />\n所以無乜必要<br />\n都唔好係7仔叫<br />\n除非你叫之前望一望佢個area<br />\n睇到無一個透明碗裝住d麵 果d通常都有上到蓋<br />\n無先好叫 咁樣你就可以食到即煮既撈麵"},{"pid":"be270d69ab425191a0ce9ab90d693d9939287eaa","tid":1124592,"uid":146949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"七仔同OK part time好似講緊40零蚊個鐘，收幾錢佢交翻咩貨，你投訴佢佢都未驚過，肯做到個煮食環境乾乾淨淨，食唔死自己仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有要求就唔會揀便利店食嘢，就算貪方便揀便利店食嘢，微波爐叮/杯麵好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17725dac2e170a0db6db3c1a875822af6bc3f58b","tid":1124592,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人識點樣剪個調味包而又唔會剪到個 較剪污糟哂"},{"pid":"8df20ac036fad5d656a94eb2fdadd91bb7e08cc7","tid":1124592,"uid":241345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"香港便利店同日本冇得比，日本嗰啲是但揀都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7116a02fa50f529f19a8b24fb1f4ad14c4803e","tid":1124592,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"7仔撈真係最撚垃圾 邊到都好食過佢"},{"pid":"bc81fd95a0d5595392482c19c128b19c366457db","tid":1124592,"uid":11869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHZqSd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHZqSd7.png&h=8d8924ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFd07t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFd07t.png&h=698066a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完個post 即可狗衝去7仔 食飯個<br />\n原來預先整定<br />\n就咁打開個蓋 加幾粒燒買就算..........<br />\n😢😢😢"},{"pid":"2284849b08b293a594707646c7c6d7c9e740c661","tid":1124592,"uid":11869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc81fd95a0d5595392482c19c128b19c366457db","tid":1124592,"uid":11869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHZqSd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHZqSd7.png&h=8d8924ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFd07t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFd07t.png&h=698066a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完個post 即可狗衝去7仔 食飯個<br />\n原來預先整定<br />\n就咁打開個蓋 加幾粒燒買就算..........<br />\n😢😢😢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"*返"},{"pid":"4a009a615c53f0a8a0be4b1243d79b8adad04e7b","tid":1124592,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f808c9613b77277653b7ed713dea823c6bacb203","tid":1124592,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"七仔撈麵煮撚到西環浮屍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}